dct_description_sm: Map shows railroads, and parks. North oriented towards top right. Includes photographs of places of historical and tourist interest on margins. On verso: ancillary road map of Cuba with distance table in kilometers, index of international warning signs, kilometers to miles conversion, street, public and tourist sites index. Notes on: house numbering system, traffic and transit regulations; historical sites located on the main highway. "The Traffic rules of Cuba are the same as in the United States."
